node.text:
BEYOND stoked at the accomplishments we’ve made over the years with my company @stsskateco and this is definitely one of our biggest milestones! We’ve made @stsskateco decks available at select @bluetomato locations across Europe! I couldn’t thank you all enough for the support over the years! It’s absolutely amazing to see STS grow as much as it has and it’s still JUST THE BEGINNING! Hit up your local @bluetomato and grab one of our decks while you can! 

Huge shoutout to the homies that helped get this short announcement video together! @g.stoops @khayrisk8 @gavinshreds @jtmillstack @therobferg @inwardtitflip 

#ThankYouSkateboarding #STS #SpreadTheShred #BlueTomato #EuropeMarket #AvailableWorldWide #VeteranOwned

node.text:
Been working full time with @robskateacademy doing travel camps and getting back into giving back to the skateboarding community by teaching all I’ve learned over the years to the awesome youth we get at camp! I forget how much I absolutely LOVE teaching and to be able to guide these young men and women to unlock new skills in the action sports world is beyond amazing!!! Hit the link in my bio and head on over to my channel to check out the entire experience! Thank you skateboarding for everything you’ve done for me and all those you bring around! 🏆💪🏾
#ThankYouSkateboarding #STS #CoachJones #RobSkateAcademy #NewYoutubeVideo #SkateboardTeacher #SpreadTheShred

node.title: OH HOW I LOVE TEACHING SKATEBOARDING!

node.text:
BEYOND stoked at the accomplishments we’ve made over the years with my company @stsskateco and this is definitely one of our biggest milestones! We’ve made @stsskateco decks available at select @bluetomato locations across Europe! I couldn’t thank you all enough for the support over the years! It’s absolutely amazing to see STS grow as much as it has and it’s still JUST THE BEGINNING! Hit up your local @bluetomato and grab one of our decks while you can! 

Huge shoutout to the homies that helped get this short announcement video together! @g.stoops @khayrisk8 @gavinshreds @jtmillstack @therobferg @inwardtitflip 

#ThankYouSkateboarding #STS #SpreadTheShred #BlueTomato #EuropeMarket #AvailableWorldWide #VeteranOwned

Teaching and running skate camps the past few weeks over at @robskateacademy has definitely reminded me how amazing and rewarding skateboarding can be! From getting kids to drop in for the first time to other kids doing BIG senders it’s incredible watching how quickly they catch on and actually start to LOVE the sport! Huge thanks to all the young ones that come thru our program and an even bigger thank you to the parents who support it! Without you we wouldn’t be able to capture some of these moments! P.S. Everyone killed it this past week but Isaac’s progression has been INSANE and that’s why he has the most clips! 💯💯🏆🖤 #ThankYouSkateboarding #STS #SpreadTheShred #RobSkateAcademy #TravelSkateCamp #CoachJones

node.text:
Been working full time with @robskateacademy doing travel camps and getting back into giving back to the skateboarding community by teaching all I’ve learned over the years to the awesome youth we get at camp! I forget how much I absolutely LOVE teaching and to be able to guide these young men and women to unlock new skills in the action sports world is beyond amazing!!! Hit the link in my bio and head on over to my channel to check out the entire experience! Thank you skateboarding for everything you’ve done for me and all those you bring around! 🏆💪🏾
#ThankYouSkateboarding #STS #CoachJones #RobSkateAcademy #NewYoutubeVideo #SkateboardTeacher #SpreadTheShred

node.text: Skateboarding has brought a lot of absolutely incredible moments, memories and has taken me to places I never thought I’d go! Without skateboarding I have no IDEA where I would be today. I’m  so thankful for everything skating has done for me over the years and will continue to do! Shoutout to each and every one of you out there learning and grinding hard! YOU GOT THIS SHIT 💯💯💯 HAPPY NATIONAL GO SKATEBOARD DAY! Get out there and get it poppin with the homies!! 🏆🏆🎥 @gabecruz01 #NationalGoSkateboardDay #GoSkateDay #ThankYouSkateboarding #STS #Braille #Berrics #SpreadTheShred
